@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vhxeqd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.23 * v1)
    v1 = wp.abs((0.04 * 0.88))
    v0 = wp.exp(v2)
    v1 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.32) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.09)) - (0.94 + (tmp + 0.06 * v0 + 0.05)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.60)))
    v0 = ((v1 - (v2 + 0.87 / v2 + 0.97)) * wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.01)))
    data[tid] = v0
